Package io.github.msdk.datamodel.rawdata

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActivationInfo
    Represents the fragmentation information of MS/MS experiments.
    ChromatographyInfo
    Represents the chromatography information of an MS scan or a detected feature.
    IsolationInfo
    Represents the ion isolation information.
    MsFunction
    Represents one MS function, such as "Full scan", "MS/MS", "MS3", "SIM", "MRM", etc.
    MsScan
    Represents a single MS scan in a raw data file.
    RawDataFile
    Raw data file, typically obtained by loading data from one of the supported file formats.
    WritableRawDataFile
    A writable raw data file.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ActivationType
    Represents the various types of MS/MS experiments.
    MsScanType
    Represents the type of MS scan.
    PolarityType
    Represents the polarity of ionization.
    SeparationType
    Enum for different separation technologies used as a preprocessing step before the actual data point acquisition.
